  <brief_title>Relationship Between Evolution of Resting Energy Expenditure and Tumoral Response to Chemotherapy in Patients Suffering From Pancreas Cancer</brief_title>
  <acronym>EnergiePancrea</acronym>
  <official_title>Monocentric, Prospective Study Assessing the Feasibility to Use Resting Energy Expenditure by Indirect Calorimetry as Prognostic Marker of Tumoral Response to 1st Line Chemotherapy in Patients Suffering From Metastatic Pancreatic Cancer</official_title>
