  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether evolution of resting energetic expenditure
      is a predictive marker of tumoral response for patients suffering from metastatic pancreatic
      cancer and treated with 1st line of chemotherapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
